      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="light-grey-band my-3">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="offset-md-3 col-md-6 text-center lead">
        <h2 data-scroll="toggle(.fromTopIn, .fromTopOut) once">Our Philosophy</h2>
        <div data-scroll="toggle(.fromBottomIn, .fromBottomOut) offset(0,-250px) once">
        <p>We are the biggest and best student night in the UK.</p>
        <p>The core idea behind the CRISIS brand is that of total inclusion. It is a student night for all students. It's that one night of the week where you are guaranteed to see all your friends in one place and share in the same experience.</p>
        <p>We believe that the happy memories that you create whilst at University will stay with you for life (at least those memories that make it past 24hrs anyway!). And to that end we work hard to make sure everything we do helps to make those moments special.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

